thread.title: KARYN
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by KARYN

author: KARYN
title: KARYN
text:
We hired a Kia Cerato for our 2 week holiday on the sunshine Coast, Queensland.
Redspot had a pick up counter in the airport. The service was quick and efficient and the car was waiting outside.
Our car was neat, clean and a late model, which drove beautifully.
There were no hidden costs and we were happy with the service.
